snippet: Graeme McDowell opened with three straight birdies and finished strong for a six-under 66 to take a three-shot lead in the World Challenge in Thousand Oaks, Calif.
lead_paragraph: Graeme McDowell opened with three straight birdies and finished strong for a six-under 66 to take a three-shot lead in the World Challenge in Thousand Oaks, Calif.

headline.seo: Graeme McDowell Opens Lead at World Challenge
